document.full_text: the united states is not expected to experience "any harmful levels" of radiation from japan's earthquake-hit nuclear power reactors, the u.s. nuclear regulatory commission said on sunday.
document.title: u.s. won't feel radiation from japan: u.s. nuclear agency
